<Layout title="Building the Future of Vietnamese Bouldering: Partner with Us for UNBOX 2026">
  <article style="max-width:900px;margin:48px auto;padding:32px;background:#FAFAFA;color:#111827;border-radius:8px;">
    <header>
      <h1 style="font-size:34px;margin-bottom:8px;">Building the Future of Vietnamese Bouldering: Partner with Us for UNBOX 2026</h1>
      <time datetime="2026-05-26">May 26, 2026</time>
    </header>

    <div style="margin-top:18px;">
      <div style="width:100%;aspect-ratio:3/2;overflow:hidden;border-radius:8px;">
        <img src="/assets/boulder-box-update-2026.avif" alt="UNBOX 2026" style="width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;display:block;" />
      </div>
    </div>

    <section style="margin-top:20px;">
      <p>At Boulder Box Saigon, we have always believed that a gym is more than just walls, holds, and mats. It is a living, breathing community. As we look toward the future of indoor bouldering in Vietnam, we are thrilled to announce our next major milestone: UNBOX 2026.</p>

      <p>We are looking for partners, brands, and visionaries who believe in the power of community to join us as sponsors for this one-of-a-kind festival.</p>

      <h3>The Concept: What is UNBOX?</h3>
      <p><strong>UNBOX:</strong> beyond convention, beyond the expected.</p>

      <p>The name represents a departure from the ordinary. In a world where fitness can sometimes feel repetitive, UNBOX is a statement. We are breaking out of the standard competitive mold to create an event that challenges the mind just as much as the body.</p>

      <p>Our gym has always set itself apart by focusing on technical, movement-focused routes. We do not just set problems for power; we set them for the puzzle. We care deeply about the true spirit of bouldering culture, and UNBOX 2026 is the ultimate expression of that love.</p>

      <h3>Culture and Community First</h3>
      <p>Bouldering has many different aspects, from fitness to extreme sport. But for us at Boulder Box, community and culture will always come first.</p>

      <p>We are still a small gym, and we are proud of our roots. There are definitely many things we still need to improve, and we learn something new every single day. Even so, alongside our dedicated team, our goal remains unchanged: we want to grow hand-in-hand with the indoor bouldering community and culture right here in Vietnam.</p>

      <p>We view UNBOX not just as a competition, but as a festival celebrating the grit, creativity, and connection that makes our community so special.</p>

      <h3>Why Sponsor UNBOX 2026?</h3>
      <p>By partnering with Boulder Box, your brand will connect directly with an active, highly engaged, and rapidly growing audience of students, young professionals, and international creators in Saigon.</p>

      <p>We are creating tailored sponsorship packages that go beyond traditional logo placement. We want to offer our partners:</p>

      <ul>
        <li><strong>Authentic Engagement:</strong> Direct interaction with over 1,000+ active community members.</li>
        <li><strong>Creative Collaboration:</strong> Opportunities for unique product placements, interactive booths, and custom challenges during the festival.</li>
        <li><strong>Digital Reach:</strong> Visibility across our growing social media channels and community network.</li>
      </ul>

      <p>Together with the people who believe in what we are trying to build, we are going to make this festival something truly special.</p>

      <p>IYKYK. (If you know, you know.)</p>

      <h3>Let’s Build Together</h3>
      <p>If your brand shares our passion for movement, growth, and community, we would love to have you on board.</p>

      <p>To receive our official Sponsorship Deck and discuss how we can create a meaningful partnership, please reach out to us at contact@bbo.fitness or send us a direct message on our social media channels.</p>

      <p>Let's unbox the potential of Vietnamese bouldering together.</p>

      <h3>Sponsorship Packages</h3>
      <p>We offer three tiers of sponsorship to fit your brand's goals. We gladly accept contributions in the form of cash, services, products, or vouchers.</p>

      <h4>🥇 Platinum Package</h4>
      <p><strong>Value:</strong> 20,000,000 VND</p>
      <p><strong>Benefits:</strong> Branded logo printed on official event T-shirts and Tote bags, branded collaboration stickers, physical banners placed at the gym, dedicated social media posts, and event appreciation videos.</p>

      <h4>🥈 Gold Package</h4>
      <p><strong>Value:</strong> 15,000,000 VND</p>
      <p><strong>Benefits:</strong> Branded collaboration stickers, physical banners placed at the gym, dedicated social media posts, and event appreciation videos.</p>

      <h4>🥉 Silver Package</h4>
      <p><strong>Value:</strong> 7,000,000 VND</p>
      <p><strong>Benefits:</strong> Branded collaboration stickers, dedicated social media posts, and event appreciation videos.</p>

      <h3>Preferred Partner Contributions</h3>
      <p>To ensure this festival brings maximum value to our climbers, we are highly interested in collaborating with brands that align with our lifestyle. Our preferred services, products, and vouchers include:</p>

      <ul>
        <li><strong>Gym Essentials:</strong> Climbing holds and climbing volumes.</li>
        <li><strong>Technical Expertise:</strong> Professional route-setting services.</li>
        <li><strong>Athlete Wellness:</strong> Health and sport-related products.</li>
        <li><strong>Community Perks:</strong> Health and sport-related vouchers.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

